e Marguerite de Turenne在法國波特-哈倫斯哈倫特結婚。他們至少是1個兒子的父母。他去世於1148年在法國波特-哈倫斯維安享年38歲。"},"zh-hans":{"1110–1148":"1110年–1148年","1102–Male":"1102年–殁","–1148":"–1148年","1120–1173":"1120年–1173年","1135–1199":"1135年–1199年","–Male":"殁","–Female":"殁","before 1147":"1147年之前","1148":"1148年","1135":"1135年","1102":"1102年","before 1100":"1100年之前","1199":"1199年","1110":"1110年","1120":"1120年","about 1135":"大约1135年","1173":"1173年","Limoges, Haute-Vienne, Limousin, France":"法国利姆辛豪-維安利莫格斯","Europe":"艾歐洛","Limoges, Vienne, Poitou-Charentes, France":"法国波特-哈倫斯維安","Charente, Poitou-Charentes, France":"法国波特-哈倫斯哈倫特","Limoges, Haute-Vienne, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France":"法国努維勒-阿吉泰豪-維安利莫格斯","lifeSummary":"Adhémar de Limoges IV是Archembaud IV de Turenne和HERBERGA LIMOJSKAYA的儿子，于1110年出生在法国利姆辛豪-維安利莫格斯。他于1147年之前与Countesse Marguerite de Turenne在法国波特-哈倫斯哈倫特结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。他去世于1148年在法国波特-哈倫斯維安享年38岁。"},"hr":{"1110–1148":"1110.–1148.","1102–Male":"1102–preminuo","–1148":"–1148.","1120–1173":"1120–1173","1135–1199":"1135–1199","–Male":"preminuo","–Female":"preminula","before 1147":"prije 1147.","1148":"1148.","1135":"1135","1102":"1102","before 1100":"prije 1100.","1199":"1199","1110":"1110.","1120":"1120","about 1135":"oko 1135.","1173":"1173","Limoges, Haute-Vienne, Limousin, France":"Limoges, Haute-Vienne, Limousin, Francuska","Europe":"Europe","Limoges, Vienne, Poitou-Charentes, France":"Vienne, Poitou-Charentes, Francuska","Charente, Poitou-Charentes, France":"Charente, Poitou-Charentes, Francuska","Limoges, Haute-Vienne, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France":"Limoges, Haute-Vienne, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, Francuska"},"cs":{"1110–1148":"1110–1148","1102–Male":"1102–Zesnulý","–1148":"–1148","1120–1173":"1120–1173","1135–1199":"1135–1199","–Male":"Zesnulý","–Female":"Zesnulá","before 1147":"před 1147","1148":"1148","1135":"1135","1102":"1102","before 1100":"před 1100","1199":"1199","1110":"1110","1120":"1120","about 1135":"okolo 1135","1173":"1173","Limoges, Haute-Vienne, Limousin, France":"Limoges, Haute-Vienne, Limousin, F